es.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mechanics and Gameplay</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Yours Truly features fundamental platforming mechanics like jumping and climbing puzzles, along with various collectibles </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The negative emotions Liam experiences are represented as distinct levels and bosses </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Narrative </h2><br>Yours Truly explores themes of happiness and fulfillment through various psychological and philosophical perspectives. This narrative-driven platformer aims to connect, teach, and inspire players by sharing universal experiences of hope, pain, struggle, and aspiration<br>Players must skillfully and cleverly take control of Liam to help him find himself through his journey. Throughout this strange place, players will find progressively challenging obstacles, puzzles, side quests, and hidden encounters that will lead Liam home.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836350/extras/33a9a2f24b6b65044d25f2315e0b547e.webp?t=1772035734\" width=693 height=29 /></span>",
